		<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>m</unclear>m<unclear>ai</unclear> patiṉ aiṅ-kaḻañcu poṉ koṇṭu kaṭavōm
	</p>

	<p>
		ip-poṉṉā<unclear>l kaḻañ</unclear>
		<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>ciṉ vāy</unclear> m<choice><orig>u</orig><reg>ū</reg></choice>ṉṟu mañcāṭi-p palicai-y-āka-<unclear>y i</unclear>vv-āṭṭai <unclear>Ai</unclear>ppaci mutal āṟāṟu tiṅ
